GRABCAR DRIVER CHEATS LADY OF $36 EVEN WHEN SHE DIDN'T USE HIS SERVICE   
<Facebook complaint by Victoria Yeo> Advertisement

I COULDN'T CANCEL THE BOOKING ON MY END AND INFORMED HIM NICELY TO HELP ME CANCEL. 
HE HAD THE CHEEK TO CLICK THAT I WAS BEING PICKED UP ALREADY AND CHARGED ME $36. 
PLEASE BLACKLIST HIM, NO INTEGRITY Editor's Note:
